blueprint_book.label: [item=laser-turret] Flame Funnel Lasers
blueprint_book.description:
It is not worth swapping to lasers until multiple damage and attack speed techs are complete. Laser dmg  4 and laser shooting speed 4 are required for substantial behemoth resitance.

Lasers should be used for logistical convenience. Guns offer vastly superior defensive capabilities. A third laser turret can be used to strengthen behemoth resistance, but it's better to use guns if additional defense is required.

Generally requires yellow techs to handle large counterattacks from artillery.
